        {
            "title": "半日收市︱重越二萬三 恒指半日升464點報23080點 中米續破頂 阿里為升市最大功臣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國家主席習近平昨出席民企座談會並與多家民企大佬見面，疊加AI應用憧憬繼續利好大市氣氛，港股今早成功重越23000點關。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/675x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/202502013_CH_source-web_xi.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/675x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/202502013_CH_source-web_xi.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">多隻大型民企股今早均受追捧，尤其是有份參與昨天民企座談會的企業股份。小米(01810)便再次破頂創歷史新高；阿里巴巴(09988)則對恒生指數貢獻最多進賬；騰訊(00700)、美團(03690)與比亞迪(01211)均跑贏大市。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/675x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/202502013_CH_source-web_xi.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/675x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/202502013_CH_source-web_xi.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103130_source-web_快手-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103130_source-web_快手-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/675x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/202502013_CH_source-web_xi.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">習近平與騰訊創辦人馬化騰握手。央視新聞</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：小米官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103130_source-web_快手-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：快手官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指今早輕微高開48點後，初段雖然短暫倒跌最多8點，但回吐至22608點便有支持，開市不久即重現反覆向上走勢，於上午10時半過後僅數分鐘終於升穿23000點，隨後升幅略為收斂並於23000點之下整固，尾段再發力重越23000點；恒指中午收報23080點，升464點或2.05%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數跑贏大市，半日升167點或3.04%，報5666點；國企指數也升190點或2.29%，報8513點。主板半日成交1759.21億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升484點，報23121點，高水41點。科指期貨升170點，報5673點，高水7點。國指期貨升192點，報8527點，高水13點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">昨天多位大型民企大佬出席民企座談會，當中包括阿里巴巴創始人馬雲、騰訊主席兼首席執行官馬化騰、小米董事長兼首席首行官雷軍、比亞迪董事長王傳福、美團董事長兼首席執行官王興。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述民企股份均成今早市場焦點，其中小米獲中信里昂唱好，將投資評級由「跑贏大市」升至「高確信跑贏大市」，目標價由40元大幅上調至56.5元，對集團今明兩年經調整淨利潤預測，亦分別調升10%及15%。該股今早再創新高，曾升上48.15元，漲6.64%；中午收報47.8元，仍升5.87%，在藍籌升幅榜排第4位。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雷軍擔任主席兼非執行董事的金山軟件(03888)與同系金山雲(03896)則高開低走，金山軟件微升0.9%，報44.85元；金山雲尚能跑贏大市，升2.72%，報10.56元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴則是今日升市最大功臣，該股半日漲4.34%，報127.5元，單一股份已為恒指提供99點升幅。同系阿里健康(00241)更升7.12%，報6.02元，與阿里巴巴分別位列藍籌升幅榜的第3名及第6名。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">騰訊也持續昨天的升勢，最高曾見512.5元，漲18.9元或3.83%；中午收報510.5元，升16.9元或3.42%。美團也升3.91%，報175.5元；比亞迪升2.48%，報364元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">在上述股份中，除了金山系外，其餘全部今早交投均躋身主板股份成交額頭10位，騰訊與阿里巴巴半日成交均過百億元，居首的騰訊成交169.09億元，阿里巴巴交投也達135.27億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101224__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於藍籌升幅榜首，則落在快手(01024)身上，該股半日飆9.7%，報58.8元，半日成交也達47.04億元。京東健康(06618)以9.19%升幅位居藍籌升幅榜次席，中午收報36.85元；同系京東(09618)則跑輸大市，升0.96%，報158.6元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：快手官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103130_source-web_快手-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：快手官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230713-103130_source-web_快手-3_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：快手官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">將於今日收市後派成績表的百度(09888)，今早依然跑輸大市，僅反彈1.06%，報90.8元。明天中午公布業績的滙控(00005)則再創3年高位，收報86.95元，升1.7%；同系恒生銀行(00011)則逆市跌0.67%，報104.3元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">車股也有追捧，吉利汽車(00175)大股東吉利控股與雷諾於巴西達成戰略合作框架協議，該股乘勢升5.21%，報17.76元。理想汽車(02015)也升4.08%，報104.7元；小鵬汽車(09868)升4.36%，報69.45元；蔚來(09866)升2.3%，報35.6元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14714271-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e4%ba%8c%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%8d%87464%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b123080%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%b3%e7%ba%8c",
