        {
            "title": "港股升穿23000點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股今早持續揚升，恒生指數於上午10時30分過後數分鐘重越23000點關口。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 (圖片來源：港交所官網)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 (圖片來源：港交所官網)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250203_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 (圖片來源：港交所官網)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至上午10時40分，恒指報23016點，升399點或1.77%；恒生科技指數升134點或2.45%，報5633點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股領漲大市，小米(01810)再創新高，升超過6%；阿里巴巴(09988)亦升約5%；騰訊(00700)升逾2%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230914_FI_source-web_01810-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
